modShortDescription: All zombies can be harvested for the same items you would get from a zombie dog. Get going on those farm plots and hobo stews!
modDescription:
All zombies can be harvested for the same items you would get from a [zombie](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) dog. Get going on those farm plots and hobo stews!

This mod works on servers with no client side installation necessary, or on single player games.

**[Download](https://imadeyoursite.com/7days/BModZombieHarvest.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/24958-brians-mods-for-alpha-196/).

**Credits:** [Dhlmaster](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/dhlmaster/)
